This is an Android app that allows simple conversion between Imperial
and Metric units. To use, first install it on your device and open it.
Then first put in the unit you want to convert from in the first drop-
down menu, and the unit you want to convert to in the second. Notice 
that the second menu changes according to your choice in the first
one.

Next, enter the amount you want to convert in the field that says
"Enter Units Here!". Then press the "Convert!" button and enjoy your
new units.